###############################################
FileSystem Connector Module
###############################################

Maintainer Contact
-----------------------------------------------
Marcus Nyeholt

<marcus (at) silverstripe (dot) com (dot) au>

Requirements
-----------------------------------------------
SilverStripe 2.4.x
External Content module

Documentation
-----------------------------------------------

See http://doc.silverstripe.org/doku.php?id=module:external-content-newconnector
which is the source of this module

* Extract the archive to your SilverStripe root folder in a folder called "filesystem-connector". Run /dev/build. 
* Navigate to the "External Content" and create a new FileSystemContentSource
connector.
* Add in the FolderPath of a location beneath base_url, relative to the base_url
value


Quick Usage Overview
-----------------------------------------------

See the external-content README
